<hymn_number>403</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 áo xiáng de de fāng shì tiān kōng jiān nán de de fāng shì jiǎo xià de lù jìng,
 jiè bēi qīng liáng shuǐ xǐ qù yī lù fēng chén wǒ men yòu zài zhǔ lǐ xiāng féng
 tóng mìng yùn tóng mài bó dōu yào yǒu kuān guǎng de xīn xiōng
 zhǐ yǒu wǒ men tóng xīn bìng jiān xiàng qián zǒu, zhǔ de zhǐ yì bì dìng hēng tōng.</lyrics>
<title>áo xiáng de de fāng shì tiān kōng 迦南403</title>
</song>